description: The MSCI GCC Countries ex Select Securities Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies listed in Gulf countries, excluding certain securities with foreign ownership restrictions Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI GCC Select Swap UCITS ETF 1C
